<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-7421] CompoundSparseCellName/WithCollection report smaller heap sizes than actual</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7421</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Class relies on sizing of super class, which doesn&apos;t take into consideration it&apos;s own foot print, along with it&apos;s excess fields.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12722703">CASSANDRA-7421</key>
            <summary>CompoundSparseCellName/WithCollection report smaller heap sizes than actual</summary>
